        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-top:4px;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üá≤üá≥ Mongolia - Expected vote of confidence.</strong> Mongolia‚Äôs PM Oyun-Erdene is facing a confidence vote amid uproar over his son‚Äôs lavish lifestyle. It is raising concerns about corruption and inequality. Protesters and political opponents accuse him of hypocrisy, while allies claim authoritarian-leaning forces are undermining him (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-9-mongolian-politics" target="_blank">Mongolian politics</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üáµüá∏ Palestine - Scenes of chaos.</strong> Many desperate Palestinians surged into a US-Israeli-backed aid site in Rafah, Gaza, overwhelming staff amid severe shortages. Aid workers distributed 8,000 food boxes using biometric checks and warnings. Chaos broke out, prompting Israeli warning shots. Critics say the Gaza Humanitarian Foundation bypasses humanitarian norms and undermines UN-led aid, further politicizing relief efforts (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-10-chaos-ensues" target="_blank">chaos ensues</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üá¨üáß UK - King speaks to Canada‚Äôs parliament.</strong> King Charles‚Äôs speech to the Canadian parliament affirmed Canada‚Äôs sovereignty and democratic values amid Trump‚Äôs calls to annex the country. The speech, part of a two-day visit, called for defense, economic independence, and unity. PM Mark Carney echoed the message, warning against overreliance on the US and asserting Canada‚Äôs sovereign path forward (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-11-the-king-s-speech" target="_blank">the king‚Äôs speech</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üá∫üá≤ USA - Trump losing patience.</strong> 
           Trump is growing frustrated with Vladimir Putin‚Äôs refusal to commit to peace talks over Ukraine, warning that the Russian leader is ‚Äúplaying with fire.‚Äù Despite harsh rhetoric, Trump remains undecided on whether to impose sanctions. While lawmakers see a possibility of pushing sanctions legislation forward, many are hesitant to make a move without Trump‚Äôs formal support (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-12-ir-is-tricky" target="_blank">IR is tricky</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üá∏üáæ Syria - Discussions with Israel.</strong> 
            Israel and Syria held direct, face-to-face talks to reduce border tensions, a significant shift after decades of hostility. The regional intelligence source described Trump's engagement with Ahmed al-Sharaa as a pivotal part of a realignment in US policy that upset Israel's post-Assad strategy of exploiting Syria's fragmentation (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-13-mystery-talks" target="_blank">mystery talks</a>). 
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding-bottom:6px;">
           <strong>üá∫üá¶ Ukraine - Zelenskyy met Merz.</strong> 
            Zelenskyy met with German Chancellor Friedrich Merz in Berlin. Merz has pledged support for Ukraine by helping Kyiv produce long-range missiles. However, he avoided naming the Taurus missile. The Taurus has a range of 310 miles and could reach deeper into Russian territory than other far-range missiles.(<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-29-may-25-worldwide-14-new-era-in-german-defense" target="_blank">German defense cooperation</a>).
          </p>
